Class Generator

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.diceware.Generator

  • public class Generator
extends Object
    Class for creating random arrays of strings or random words utilizing a random number generator and lists of short words.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Generator(String[] words, Random rng)
      Recieves a list of words, a random number generator and size of array necessary as inputs then generates a randomized array of said length and returns.

        public Generator(String[] words,
                 Random rng)
          throws NullPointerException,
                 IllegalArgumentException
        Recieves a list of words, a random number generator and size of array necessary as inputs then generates a randomized array of said length and returns.

        Parameters:
        words - String of words to submit into generator.
        rng - Random number generator.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if you don't provide a random number generator or a words list.
        IllegalArgumentException - if you haven't included words in word list.

      • next

        public String[] next(int numWords,
                     boolean duplicatesAllowed)
              throws NegativeArraySizeException,
                     IllegalArgumentException
        This method allows user to decide whether or not to include duplicate word from list when randomizing the array. It uses the same concept as the first method. User inputs list of words, rng, size of array, and includes true or false for duplicates.

        Parameters:
        numWords - String of words to submit for randomizing.
        duplicatesAllowed - indicates words can be duplicated from list.
        Returns:
        Returns randomized array generated by rng.
        Throws:
        NegativeArraySizeException - if attempting to generate an array of negative value.
        IllegalArgumentException - if requesting an array that is of higher value than words in list and no duplicates are allowed.
